Introduction

Roh Jisun is a South Korean singer-songwriter under HYBE Labels. She was the center and one of the lead dancers of the girl group fromis_9.

Jisun competed in the survival show "Idol School," where she ended up in the 1st place, earning her spot in the group fromis_9.

She debuted as a member of fromis_9 on January 24, 2018, with the mini album To. Heart.
